From Alan Richardson Subject Now available Now available xvertext Summary xvertext provides you with four functions to draw strings at any angle in an X window previous versions were limited to vertical text Rotation is still achieved using XImages but the notion of rotating a whole font first has been What's new I've added a cache which keeps a copy of previously rotated strings thus speeding up Where can I get it contrib now Alan Richardson You don't have to be School of Maths Physical Sciences old to be wise of Sussex Brighton ENGLAND Judas Priest UK elsewhere